snippet.title: Pikmin 251: Official Release trailer
snippet.description:
After 9 months in development, the full release of Pikmin 251 is finally here!
Play through an all new story and all new worlds from pikmin 2, with all kinds of new surprises.
New treasures, new challenge and versus stage, and much more!

Link to download pikmin 251 installer:
https:/bit.ly/pikmin251

Pikmin 251 Discord Server: https://discord.gg/WHSaSS5

(Nintendo police don't read this part)
If you absolutely cannot get the installer to work, or cannot find a vanilla pikmin 2 US iso, I have provided a full 2.3.0 iso download here. Please only use this as a last resort though.
bit.ly/pikmin251iso
